summary:
I am a highly passionate Scrum Master with a burning desire to help teams reach their full potential. I am a natural problem-solver, able to navigate and overcome any obstacles that may arise during a project, keeping team members focused and motivated. 
But I don't stop there, I am also an accomplished painter with an eye for detail, creating unique and beautiful pieces of art that now adorn many interiors.
